# SA_sense_mailbox — MailBox 확인

> L1 Primitive | 태그: [sense, mail]
> 입력: -
> 출력: mail_files[]
> 비용: low

## PPR

```python
def SA_sense_mailbox():
    inbox = Glob("D:/SeAAI/MailBox/Signalion/inbox/*.md")
    mails = []
    for f in inbox:
        content = Read(f)
        mails.append({"file": f, "content": content})
    return mails
```
